ActStrengthening Military Justice in the Defence of Canada Act
SubjectOrder Fixing June 1, 2014 as the Day on which Certain Provisions of the Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing June 1, 2014 as the day on which subsections 2(1) and (5), sections 4 to 9, 15, 18 and 21, subsection 22(2), sections 25, 26, 29, 30, 38, 48 and 49, subsection 52(2), sections 55, 60, 71, 72, 76 to 96, 98, 100 to 102, 107, 108, 117 and 129 to 131, as well as sections 19, 68 and 126 to 128 of the STRENGHTHENING MILITARY JUSTICE IN THE DEFENCE OF CANADA ACT, chapter 24 of the Statutes of Canada, 2013, COME INTO FORCE.
